---

<section class="py-24 bg-linear-to-br from-sage/10 to-mint/10">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<span
				class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4"
				>The Science</span
			>
			<h2
				class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-forest mb-4 tracking-tight"
			>
				Why Grass-Fed Is Better For You
			</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				It's not marketingâ€”it's science. Here's what happens when cattle
				eat what nature intended.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<!-- Omega-3 -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M19.5 3.5L18 2l-1.5 1.5L15 2l-1.5 1.5L12 2l-1.5 1.5L9 2 7.5 3.5 6 2 4.5 3.5 3 2v20l1.5-1.5L6 22l1.5-1.5L9 22l1.5-1.5L12 22l1.5-1.5L15 22l1.5-1.5L18 22l1.5-1.5L21 22V2l-1.5 1.5zM19 19H5V5h14v14zM9 7h6v2H9V7zm0 4h6v2H9v-2zm0 4h4v2H9v-2z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
					<span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-forest"
						>2-4x</span
					>
					<span class="text-sage font-semibold">More</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Omega-3 Fatty Acids
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Grass-fed beef contains significantly more heart-healthy
					omega-3s than grain-fed. The same good fats found in salmon
					and fish oil.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- CLA -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
					<span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-forest"
						>500%</span
					>
					<span class="text-sage font-semibold">Higher</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					CLA Content
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Conjugated Linoleic Acid (CLA) is linked to improved heart
					health, reduced body fat, and better immune function.
					Grass-fed beef is one of the best natural sources.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Vitamins -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9L12 3zm6.82 6L12 12.72 5.18 9 12 5.28 18.82 9zM17 15.99l-5 2.73-5-2.73v-3.72L12 15l5-2.73v3.72z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
					<span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-forest"
						>10x</span
					>
					<span class="text-sage font-semibold">More</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Beta-Carotene
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					The precursor to Vitamin A that supports eye health, immune
					function, and skin health. Grass-fed beef's yellow fat is a
					sign of this nutrient density.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Vitamin E -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
					<span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-forest"
						>3x</span
					>
					<span class="text-sage font-semibold">More</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Vitamin E
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					A powerful antioxidant that protects cells from damage.
					Grass-fed beef is a natural source of this essential
					nutrient.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- No Hormones -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zM4 12c0-4.42 3.58-8 8-8 1.85 0 3.55.63 4.9 1.69L5.69 16.9C4.63 15.55 4 13.85 4 12zm8 8c-1.85 0-3.55-.63-4.9-1.69L18.31 7.1C19.37 8.45 20 10.15 20 12c0 4.42-3.58 8-8 8z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
					<span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-forest"
						>Zero</span
					>
					<span class="text-sage font-semibold">Added</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Hormones or Antibiotics
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Our cattle are never given growth hormones or routine
					antibiotics. Just grass, water, and the occasional scratch
					behind the ears.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Better Ratio -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM9 17H7v-7h2v7zm4 0h-2V7h2v10zm4 0h-2v-4h2v4z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-3">
					<span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-forest"
						>1:3</span
					>
					<span class="text-sage font-semibold">Ratio</span>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Omega 6:3 Balance
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Grain-fed beef can have ratios of 20:1. Our grass-fed beef
					maintains a healthy 1:3 ratio, reducing inflammation and
					supporting overall health.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-16 text-center">
			<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Sources: Journal of Animal Science, Nutrition Journal, European
				Journal of Clinical Nutrition. Individual results may vary based
				on overall diet and lifestyle.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

